  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You may spend a spell point to apply this word to an object or weapon. If placed on an object, it counts as a divine focus for all purposes. If placed on a weapon, it becomes chaotic, evil, good, or lawful, as you choose, overcomes that type of damage reduction, and deals an additional 2d6 damage to creatures of the opposite alignment. This effect lasts as long as you concentrate, but you may always spend a spell point to allow the effect to endure for 1 minute per caster level without concentration.</p>\n",
